init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I don't know how JFK had known this, or why he might have taken it upon himself to have me rousted out of my retirement, but

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I picked up the phone and dialed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: calling to let you know your next mission.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm the only one who can save humanity from the alien invaders who have stolen our bodies and are using their consciousness to rule over us.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: at his secret time machine base.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There was a lot of information to process.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then we had to take it to the future and use it in conjunction with their own time crystals to create a super time crystal that would send out a

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Oh, outside my secret time machine base.", he replied.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It wasn't long before we struck the time crystal and successfully unearthed it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We have to get this time crystal back to the future.", I said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We arrived in the future to find that it was a terrible place full of despair and anguish.
